            <p>TOEFL iBT is one of the most popular English proficiency exams which is accepted at American and Canadian universities and education institutions abroad. It is conducted by ETS or Educational Testing Service. TOEFL stands as the full form of Test of English as a Foreign Language. ETS TOEFL exam measures the four academic English skills, which include reading, listening, speaking and writing in the setting of university.</p>
            <p>Candidates can appear for either TOEFL iBT (Internet Based Test) or TOEFL Home Edition, based on their convenience.</p>
