            <h2>TOEFL Exam Pattern 2024</h2>
            <p>TOEFL exam pattern has been divided broadly into four sections: Reading, Listening, Speaking and Writing. The more the TOEFL sample papers are practiced, the better will be TOEFL scores. Each section has a score range of 0-30, forming a total score range of 0-120. Scores shall be available online six days after the commencement of examination. ETS shall directly send the four official score reports to the institution which is selected by the students.</p>
          </div>

