            <h3>Age Requirements</h3>
            <p>ETS is the conducting body of the TOEFL exam and has not particularly set exam age limits for candidates who are looking to appear in exam.</p>
            <h3>Education Qualifications</h3>
            <p>ETS has not set academic qualifications as part of eligibility for TOEFL exam, however by extension of admission to universities situated abroad, candidates should ideally have passed 10+2 from a recognized board for eligibility to apply to universities abroad for higher education.</p>
