            <h2>TOEFL Exam Preparation 2024</h2>
            <p>For TOEFL Exam Preparation, there are two approaches: Self-study and attending coaching classes. Both methods of studying have different benefits and no one way is superior to the other. If money is considered to be the prime concern, then self-study by TOEFL books and resources may be a better option. Secondly, if you need professional guidance to ensure an advantage for TOEFL exam preparation, then enrollment in TOEFL coaching center will be a better option.</p>
            <p>TOEFL Test analyzes the ability to understand the English level which is at the university level. Four sections are used for judging the reading, writing, listening and speaking abilities. In the process of preparation, candidates should understand the format of the TOEFL test as well as TOEFL scores.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- TOEFL Tips Section -->
