            <p>Candidates are advised to follow important TOEFL exam day tips to be able to perform good in the day of exam. Good preparation for the exam starts a day prior to TOEFL exam day. Candidates are required to sleep early and feel fresh during the TOEFL exam day.</p>
            <div class="highlight-box">
              <h3>TOEFL Tips 2024</h3>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Arrive Early:</strong> Aiming to arrive at least 30 minutes prior to scheduled exam time is preferred for avoiding last minute stress.</li>
                <li><strong>Bringing Required Documents:</strong> Carry your valid ID (passport or another Government ID) and TOEFL Registration confirmation.</li>
                <li><strong>Dress Comfortable:</strong> Dressing comfortably by wearing layers for accommodating different room temperatures, comfort of which can help to focus better in exam and do well.</li>
                <li><strong>Familiarizing With the Format:</strong> By reviewing the TOEFL format and the types of questions asked can help to be more comfortable during exam.</li>
                <li><strong>Practice Time Management:</strong> Practicing time management and managing the time well can ensure completing the questions on time.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
